15:49.000 --> 15:50.447
♪ Get down tonight ♪

15:50.517 --> 15:53.379
♪ Get down tonight ♪

16:05.447 --> 16:07.379
[ electronics sparking]

16:07.447 --> 16:09.344
[ audience hooting]

16:09.413 --> 16:11.379
Poor guy.

16:11.447 --> 16:14.000
Maybe you'd feel better
if I had a drink.

16:15.274 --> 16:16.447
Crummy keg.

16:16.517 --> 16:18.172
It's completely...

16:18.240 --> 16:19.413
Oh, you're a robot.

16:19.481 --> 16:20.861
Don't stop.

16:20.931 --> 16:23.136
Attention, happening robots.

16:23.206 --> 16:26.344
Who's got what it takes
to party with Nixon?

16:26.413 --> 16:29.688
[ cheering and applause]

16:29.758 --> 16:32.931
You fellows enjoy yourselves
for the next two hours

16:33.000 --> 16:35.206
and be sure not
to leave the island

16:35.274 --> 16:37.000
uh, for at least two hours.

16:37.067 --> 16:39.413
I'm going out
to pick up some smokes.

16:39.481 --> 16:40.688
Really good smokes.

16:40.758 --> 16:42.481
Two hours.

16:42.551 --> 16:44.965
[ cheering and applause]

16:45.033 --> 16:48.620
Okay, headless body of Agnew,
let's blow this joint.

16:48.688 --> 16:50.724
Bah!

16:54.344 --> 16:57.379
[ whirring]

16:58.586 --> 17:01.102
Do you want
to dance?

17:01.172 --> 17:03.102
No, I-I'm not really
in the...

17:03.172 --> 17:05.136
You know you
want to.

17:05.205 --> 17:07.862
[ metal clanging and groaning]

17:07.931 --> 17:10.862
WERNSTROM:
Per your orders,
I modified my mirror

17:10.931 --> 17:13.034
to fire a colossal
electromagnetic pulse

17:13.103 --> 17:14.517
at the Galapagos.

17:14.586 --> 17:18.103
Every robot will be instantly
and painfully terminated.

17:18.172 --> 17:20.309
Now, for your part
of the bargain?

17:20.378 --> 17:22.758
Ah, ooh, very well.

17:22.826 --> 17:25.517
Agnew, you belong
to Wernstrom now.

17:25.586 --> 17:27.792
[ monstrous growl]

17:27.862 --> 17:29.550
I'll say good-bye now.

17:29.619 --> 17:33.103
There ain't no turtles
where daddy's a-goin'.

17:33.172 --> 17:34.172
Don't tell anybody

17:34.240 --> 17:35.205
but Nixon's about

17:35.275 --> 17:37.240
to shut all the robots off,
and...

17:37.309 --> 17:38.448
What?!

17:38.517 --> 17:39.654
[ air raid siren blares]

17:39.723 --> 17:40.931
It's a trap.We're going to die.

17:41.000 --> 17:41.931
Oh!

17:42.000 --> 17:44.550
[ groaning and chatter]

17:44.619 --> 17:47.067
Nixon's not bringing the smokes.

17:47.136 --> 17:49.136
[ frantic beeping]

17:49.205 --> 17:50.309
[ fading beep]

17:50.378 --> 17:53.550
Shut and pay attention
to me, Bender!

17:55.034 --> 17:57.931
[ crowd quieting]

17:58.000 --> 18:00.275
Look, I love life
and its pleasures

18:00.344 --> 18:01.862
as much as anyone here

18:01.931 --> 18:03.964
except perhaps you,
Hedonismbot.

18:04.034 --> 18:06.067
[ gulping]

18:06.136 --> 18:08.240
But we need to be shut off!

18:08.309 --> 18:10.481
Especially you, Hedonismbot.

18:10.550 --> 18:12.792
[ British accent]:
I apologize for nothing!

18:12.862 --> 18:14.172
We pollute too much!

18:14.240 --> 18:17.586
We're destroying the world
and killing the turtles!

18:17.654 --> 18:19.034
To hell with the turtles.

18:19.103 --> 18:20.931
No one insults the turtles.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.448
[ smacking and groaning]

18:22.517 --> 18:23.481
[ groaning]

18:23.550 --> 18:24.619
Get 'em![ crowd cheering]

18:24.689 --> 18:25.619
Why you...

18:25.689 --> 18:29.654
[ groaning]

18:29.723 --> 18:31.792
Let the games begin!

18:31.862 --> 18:33.378
[ airy laugh]

18:33.448 --> 18:36.103
[ engine landing]

18:37.964 --> 18:40.550
[ panting]

18:40.619 --> 18:42.586
Everyone, listen!

18:42.654 --> 18:44.723
[ crowd murmuring]

18:44.792 --> 18:45.964
[ groans]

18:46.034 --> 18:47.103
Damn!

18:47.172 --> 18:49.309
I've devised a way
to save you

18:49.378 --> 18:52.275
and stop global warming
at the same time.

18:52.344 --> 18:56.000
Granted, you're
all blasting out
greenhouse gases...

18:56.067 --> 18:57.964
You're one to talk.

18:58.034 --> 18:59.205
[ groans]:
Ooh!

18:59.275 --> 19:01.240
But we can use those

19:01.309 --> 19:03.586
very gases to
save the planet.

19:03.654 --> 19:05.344
If you all vent
your exhaust

19:05.413 --> 19:07.205
directly upward
in one burst

19:07.275 --> 19:10.275
it should thrust
the Earth further
from the Sun

19:10.344 --> 19:11.826
thus cooling it.

19:11.895 --> 19:13.344
Ooh.[ murmuring]

19:13.413 --> 19:14.758
By my calculations

19:14.826 --> 19:18.000
we'll need the full force
of every last robot.

19:18.067 --> 19:19.172
So quickly

19:19.240 --> 19:21.205
everyone point
your exhaust vents

19:21.275 --> 19:23.275
straight upwards.

19:23.344 --> 19:26.034
[ metal creaking]

19:32.309 --> 19:33.481
Now, vent.

19:33.550 --> 19:35.481
Vent like the wind!

19:35.550 --> 19:37.000
[ belching]

19:37.067 --> 19:38.792
[ tense music playing]

19:42.654 --> 19:44.309
Harder! Harder!

19:44.378 --> 19:45.862
Yeah.

19:45.931 --> 19:47.205
[ grunting and belching]

19:47.275 --> 19:48.517
Why isn't this
working?

19:48.586 --> 19:51.481
Some lazy or polite robot
is holding it in.

19:51.550 --> 19:53.586
[ grunting]

19:53.654 --> 19:55.931
Help! Help!

19:56.000 --> 19:57.654
[ gases roaring]

19:57.723 --> 20:00.205
[ whirring]

20:00.275 --> 20:02.862
[ evil laugh]

20:02.931 --> 20:06.586
A billion robot lives are
about to be extinguished!

20:06.654 --> 20:09.862
Oh, the Jedis are going
to feel this one!

20:09.931 --> 20:11.481
I'm sorry, buddy.

20:11.550 --> 20:15.172
At we'll die
on our backs, helpless.

20:15.240 --> 20:16.344
Huh?

20:16.413 --> 20:18.895
What the hell are you doing?

20:20.550 --> 20:22.758
Hey are you trying
to make me look bad?

20:22.826 --> 20:25.240
[ grunting]

20:25.309 --> 20:27.826
[ tense music builds]

20:30.481 --> 20:31.619
Aha!

20:31.689 --> 20:33.826
I'm even greater
than I thought I was.

20:33.895 --> 20:37.172
And now, to fulfill my destiny.

20:37.240 --> 20:41.309
[ gases roaring]

20:43.275 --> 20:43.964
Fire!

20:44.034 --> 20:46.448
[ pulse firing]

20:46.517 --> 20:47.758
What the... ?We missed!

20:47.826 --> 20:50.136
[ angry groan]

20:51.792 --> 20:53.723
[ birds singing]

20:53.792 --> 20:56.240
[ waves crashing]

20:56.309 --> 20:59.067
Professor, for
saving the Earth

20:59.136 --> 21:00.275
and foiling me

21:00.344 --> 21:02.964
I proudly, yet
angrily present you

21:03.034 --> 21:05.448
with Earth's new
highest honor--

21:05.517 --> 21:09.481
The Polluting Medal
of Pollution.

21:09.550 --> 21:11.275
[ coughing]

21:11.344 --> 21:12.448
Thank you.

21:12.517 --> 21:14.172
I deserve this.

21:14.240 --> 21:16.172
[ cheering and applause]

21:16.240 --> 21:17.792
Hey, Professor

21:17.862 --> 21:19.448
now that the Earth's
orbit is further

21:19.517 --> 21:20.481
from the sun

21:20.550 --> 21:22.034
won't that make the year
longer?

21:22.103 --> 21:23.172
Why, yes.

21:23.240 --> 21:25.034
One week longer, to be exact.

21:25.103 --> 21:26.205
In that case

21:26.275 --> 21:28.205
I hereby declare it

21:28.275 --> 21:30.205
Robot Party Week!

21:30.275 --> 21:31.689
[ cheering and applause]

21:35.654 --> 21:37.205
♪ Me mind on fire ♪

21:37.275 --> 21:40.689
♪ Me soul on fire,
feeling hot, hot, hot ♪

21:43.275 --> 21:46.309
♪ Party people all around me ♪

21:46.378 --> 21:47.792
♪ Feeling hot, hot, hot ♪

21:47.862 --> 21:49.792
[ cheering and coughing]

21:51.758 --> 21:54.964
[ coughing continues]
